<LegalLayout
  title="Privacy Policy — BiasharaPOS"
  titleSw="Sera ya Faragha — BiasharaPOS"
  description="How BiasharaPOS collects, uses and protects the personal and business data of merchants in Tanzania."
  descriptionSw="Jinsi BiasharaPOS inavyokusanya, kutumia na kulinda data binafsi na ya biashara ya wafanyabiashara nchini Tanzania."
  path="/privacy"
  heading="Privacy Policy"
  headingSw="Sera ya Faragha"
  updated="10 June 2026"
>
  <p data-en="This Privacy Policy explains how BiasharaPOS (“we”, “us”, “our”) collects, uses and safeguards information when you use our point-of-sale application, website and related services (the “Service”). By using the Service you agree to the practices described here." data-sw="Sera hii ya Faragha inaeleza jinsi BiasharaPOS (“sisi”, “yetu”) inavyokusanya, kutumia na kulinda taarifa unapotumia programu yetu ya mauzo, tovuti na huduma zinazohusiana (“Huduma”). Kwa kutumia Huduma unakubali matumizi yaliyoelezwa hapa.">This Privacy Policy explains how BiasharaPOS (“we”, “us”, “our”) collects, uses and safeguards information when you use our point-of-sale application, website and related services (the “Service”). By using the Service you agree to the practices described here.</p>

  <h2 data-en="Information we collect" data-sw="Taarifa tunazokusanya">Information we collect</h2>
  <ul>
    <li data-en="Account details — your name, business name, phone number and email address when you register." data-sw="Maelezo ya akaunti — jina lako, jina la biashara, namba ya simu na barua pepe unapojisajili.">Account details — your name, business name, phone number and email address when you register.</li>
    <li data-en="Business data — products, prices, inventory, sales records and the fiscal receipts you generate." data-sw="Data ya biashara — bidhaa, bei, hesabu ya bidhaa, kumbukumbu za mauzo na risiti za kodi unazozalisha.">Business data — products, prices, inventory, sales records and the fiscal receipts you generate.</li>
    <li data-en="Usage data — device type, app version and basic analytics that help us improve the Service." data-sw="Data ya matumizi — aina ya kifaa, toleo la programu na takwimu za msingi zinazotusaidia kuboresha Huduma.">Usage data — device type, app version and basic analytics that help us improve the Service.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 data-en="How we use your information" data-sw="Jinsi tunavyotumia taarifa zako">How we use your information</h2>
  <p data-en="We use your information to operate the Service, process sales, generate TRA-compliant VFD receipts, provide customer support, send important service notices and improve our features. We do not sell your personal or business data to third parties." data-sw="Tunatumia taarifa zako kuendesha Huduma, kushughulikia mauzo, kuzalisha risiti za VFD zinazokubalika na TRA, kutoa msaada kwa wateja, kutuma taarifa muhimu za huduma na kuboresha vipengele vyetu. Hatuuzi data yako binafsi au ya biashara kwa watu wengine.">We use your information to operate the Service, process sales, generate TRA-compliant VFD receipts, provide customer support, send important service notices and improve our features. We do not sell your personal or business data to third parties.</p>

  <h2 data-en="Sharing &amp; disclosure" data-sw="Kushiriki na kufichua">Sharing &amp; disclosure</h2>
  <p data-en="We share data only with service providers who help us run the Service (such as payment and hosting partners), and with the Tanzania Revenue Authority where fiscalisation is legally required. We may also disclose information when required by law." data-sw="Tunashiriki data tu na watoa huduma wanaotusaidia kuendesha Huduma (kama washirika wa malipo na uhifadhi), na na Mamlaka ya Mapato Tanzania pale ufuataji kodi unapohitajika kisheria. Tunaweza pia kufichua taarifa pale sheria inapohitaji.">We share data only with service providers who help us run the Service (such as payment and hosting partners), and with the Tanzania Revenue Authority where fiscalisation is legally required. We may also disclose information when required by law.</p>

  <h2 data-en="Data security &amp; retention" data-sw="Usalama na uhifadhi wa data">Data security &amp; retention</h2>
  <p data-en="We protect your data with encryption in transit and access controls. Sales and fiscal records are retained for as long as required by Tanzanian tax law. You can request deletion of your account data, subject to those legal retention obligations." data-sw="Tunalinda data yako kwa usimbaji wakati wa usafirishaji na udhibiti wa ufikiaji. Kumbukumbu za mauzo na kodi zinahifadhiwa kwa muda unaohitajika na sheria ya kodi ya Tanzania. Unaweza kuomba kufutwa kwa data ya akaunti yako, kwa kuzingatia wajibu huo wa kisheria wa uhifadhi.">We protect your data with encryption in transit and access controls. Sales and fiscal records are retained for as long as required by Tanzanian tax law. You can request deletion of your account data, subject to those legal retention obligations.</p>

  <h2 data-en="Your rights" data-sw="Haki zako">Your rights</h2>
  <p data-en="You may access, correct or export your data, and ask us to delete information we are not legally required to keep. To exercise any of these rights, contact us at the address below." data-sw="Unaweza kufikia, kurekebisha au kupakua data yako, na kutuomba tufute taarifa ambazo hatutakiwi kisheria kuzihifadhi. Ili kutumia haki hizi, wasiliana nasi kupitia anwani iliyo hapa chini.">You may access, correct or export your data, and ask us to delete information we are not legally required to keep. To exercise any of these rights, contact us at the address below.</p>

  <h2 data-en="Contact us" data-sw="Wasiliana nasi">Contact us</h2>
  <p data-en={'Questions about this policy? Email us at <a href="mailto:hello@biashara-pos.com">hello@biashara-pos.com</a>.'} data-sw={'Maswali kuhusu sera hii? Tutumie barua pepe <a href="mailto:hello@biashara-pos.com">hello@biashara-pos.com</a>.'}>Questions about this policy? Email us at <a href="mailto:hello@biashara-pos.com">hello@biashara-pos.com</a>.</p>
</LegalLayout>
